</span></code></pre>
<p>This API lets you list all rewards associated with a certain profile.</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET /api/v1/profiles/{profile}/rewards</code></p>
<h2 id='retrieve-a-reward'>Retrieve a reward</h2>
